response.original_title: Chikara Chikarasaurus Rex: King of Sequel - Night 1
response.overview: July 30th, 2011 :: In what would prove to be their final one-on-one encounter, British wrestling legends Johnny Saint and Johnny Kidd meet in a special “World of Sport” match. A 6-woman tag sees Sara Del Rey, Daizee Haze and Makoto face Portia Perez, Mima Shimoda and Tsukasa Fujimoto! Green Ant has his much-anticipated singles bout against Tursas! Plus, the 12 Large: Summit round-robin delivers Jigsaw vs. Fire Ant and Mike Quackenbush vs. Claudio Castagnoli.
response.title: Chikara Chikarasaurus Rex: King of Sequel - Night 1
